### Hadith 2:701

*Narrated Ibn Abbas:*

I gave Zam-zam water to Allah's Apostle and he drank it while standing.
'Asia (a sub-narrator) said that 'Ikrima took the oath that on that day
the Prophet had not been standing but riding a camel.

